OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening, just the odd shower
OL,7,Faround. Then the rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be dry with variable cloud and
OL,9,Fsome lengthy clear periods.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FMany places will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome bright or sunny intervals, the
OL,13,Fodd shower across the Cairngorms. Warm
OL,14,Fin the east.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FPatchy
OL,17,Frain on Tuesday morning, a few showers
OL,18,Fin the afternoon. Mostly dry on
OL,19,FWednesday, the odd afternoon shower.
OL,20,FEarly rain on Thursday followed by a
OL,21,Ffew showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
